70
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:39,010
Besides...

71
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:46,010
Besides, what?

72
00:06:46,010 --> 00:06:47,310
Oh, nothing.

73
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:49,210
