143
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:38,610
and leave just like that.

144
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:40,310
Look at the address, Dr. Agasa.

145
00:10:40,310 --> 00:10:41,910
On the envelope that was delivered to my house,

146
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:44,810
