Who is inside

191
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,010
this house?

192
00:13:44,610 --> 00:13:49,310
I guess this is the best place to watch me and Haibara.

193
00:13:54,710 --> 00:13:58,110
I know I can handle two men,

194
00:13:58,110 --> 00:14:00,510
