208
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,570
Shut up.

209
00:15:24,570 --> 00:15:28,070
I mean I'm getting a positive turbulent rush of blood as a detective!

210
00:15:28,070 --> 00:15:30,170
Excuse me?

211
00:15:30,170 --> 00:15:32,270
